item.title: CVE-2020-14488|2024-09-17T02:06:04.474Z -- open%20source -- openclinic%20ga
item.description: OpenClinic GA 5.09.02 and 5.89.05b does not properly verify uploaded files, which may allow a low-privilege user to upload and execute arbitrary files on the system.

item.title: CVE-2020-14489|2024-09-17T01:46:22.188Z -- open%20source -- openclinic%20ga
item.description: OpenClinic GA 5.09.02 and 5.89.05b stores passwords using inadequate hashing complexity, which may allow an attacker to recover passwords using known password cracking techniques.
